{"title":"Pearl iZUMi Launches Brand Refresh Along with Spring/Summer ’24 Line","link":"https://bikerumor.com/pearl-izumi-launches-brand-refresh-spring-summer-2024-line/","date":1708621200000,"content":"<p><img width=\"1280\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Hero.jpg\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Hero.jpg 1280w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Hero-297x186.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Hero-800x500.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Hero-120x75.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Hero-768x480.jpg 768w\" /></p>\n<p>A few days ago, long-time cycling apparel brand, Pearl Izumi, released its Spring/Summer line of items on top of a brand refresh. With this new launch, Pearl Izumi hopes to “<em>inspire and empower riders to “push their limits, explore new horizons, and revel in the pure joy of cycling</em>“. </p>\n\n\n\n<p>Let’s check in to see some of the new pieces. </p>\n\n\n\n<h2>Road</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-Womens-front-black.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-Womens-front-black-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi SS24 Collection PRO Jersey Womens front black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-Womens-front-black-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-Womens-front-black-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-Womens-front-black-120x120.jpeg 120w, https:/