umor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-front-blue-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-front-blue.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-back-red.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-back-red-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi SS24 Collection PRO Jersey back red\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-back-red-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-back-red-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-back-red-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-back-red-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-PRO-Jersey-back-red.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>PRO Jersey</strong> –<strong> </strong>The new <a href=\"https://www.pearlizumi.com/collections/mens-new-arrivals/products/mens-pro-jersey-11122404?variant=43472214655147\" target=\"_blank\">Pro Jersey</a> is built with the hardcore racer/rider in mind. It’s made with premium Italian stretch fabrics, sleek bonded finishes, and Pearl’s iconic Speed Sleeve construction. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Retail: </strong>$180</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Lightweight compression mesh offers optimal breathability</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Heritage Italian fabric feels soft and silky on the skin</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Bonded, no-stitch clean hemlines offer more consistent stretch</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UPF 30 sun protection</li>\n\n\n\n<li>3 rear &amp; 1 side zippered pockets</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sizes: S, M, L, XL, XXL</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Gravel</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-black.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-black-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi SS24 Collection Expedition Merino Wool Jersey black\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-black-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-black-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-black-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-black-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-black.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-back.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-back-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi SS24 Collection Expedition Merino Wool Jersey back\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-back-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-back-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-back-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-back-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Expedition-Merino-Wool-Jersey-back.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Expedition Merino Jersey</strong> – Specifically designed for bikepackers, the new <a href=\"https://www.pearlizumi.com/collections/mens-new-arrivals/products/mens-expedition-merino-short-sleeve-jersey-11122409?variant=43438637514923\" target=\"_blank\">Expedition Merino Jersey</a> is the perfect jersey for time spent off the bike enjoying your surroundings. It is constructed with Drirelease Merino Wool which feels ultra soft to the hand. It also has natural odor-fighting properties and a sweat-wicking performance that is 4x better than cotton. The high stretch, woven sleeves add durability and comfort. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Retail: </strong>$90</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features:</strong> </p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Abrasion-resistant sleeves and bottom panel</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Standard Fit</li>\n\n\n\n<li>1 zippered utility pocket</li>\n\n\n\n<li>UPF 20</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sizes: S, M, L, XL, XXL</li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Mountain</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-palm.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-palm-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi SS24 Collection Summit PRO Glove palm\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-palm-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-palm-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-palm-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-palm-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-palm.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-ghost-knucks.jpeg\"><img width=\"800\" height=\"800\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-ghost-knucks-800x800.jpeg\" alt=\"Pearl Izumi SS24 Collection Summit PRO Glove ghost knucks\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-ghost-knucks-800x800.jpeg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-ghost-knucks-297x297.jpeg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-ghost-knucks-120x120.jpeg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-ghost-knucks-768x768.jpeg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/02/Pearl-Izumi-SS24-Collection-Summit-PRO-Glove-ghost-knucks.jpeg 1000w\" /></a></figure>\n</figure>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Summit Pro Glove</strong> – Made of lightweight materials, the <a href=\"https://www.pearlizumi.com/collections/mens-new-arrivals/products/mens-summit-pro-gloves-14142403?variant=43438490681515\" target=\"_blank\">Summit Pro Glove</a> combines durable ripstop fabrics as well as slim D30 Ghost Knuckles for added protection. </p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Retail: </strong>$50</p>\n\n\n\n<p><strong>Features: </strong></p>\n\n\n\n<ul>\n<li>Adjustable hook and loop cuff</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Moisture-wicking Transfer fabrics on the back of the hand</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Touchscreen-compatible Clarino® palm material</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Silicone gripper on thumb and forefingers</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Laser perforated palm for additional breathability</li>\n\n\n\n<li>Sizes: XS, S, M, L, XL, </li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n<h2>Bikestyle</h2>\n\n\n\n<figure>\n<figure><a href=\"https://bik